CityShiftBench review artifact license summary

Copyright (c) 2026 Anonymous Authors

This repository contains several kinds of material with different license
obligations. The license terms below are intended for the anonymous NeurIPS
Evaluations and Datasets review artifact and should be preserved in any public
release.

1. Original code and scripts

Original source code, plotting scripts, table-generation scripts, and
experiment wrappers written for CityShiftBench are released under the MIT
License:

